result.title: Looking for some Project
result.content:
Hii everyone,

I am looking for some open-source implemented project of some latest idea of around 2015-2016 as i need it as part of my coursework in my university. Following projects would be suitable : 1) Open source project along with code and some sort of documentation from which i can understand that project and try to implement it on my own. 2) Some project which is implemented on the basis of some research paper.

If the project topic is relatively new i.e it is of 2015-2016 that it would be really helpful.

Thanks in advance!!!

Happy Coding!!!
